snippet.title: People across the Country are Excited to Get New Currency Notes in Exchange of Rs 500, Rs 1000 Notes

localized.description:
People across the country are exicted to get new currency notes in exchange of Rs 500, Rs 1000 notes. All ATMs will open on November 11 across the country. People can withdraw only Rs 2000 cash from the ATMs per card. On 10th November, all banks have opened and peoples struggled to exchange and deposit Rs 500 and Rs 1000 currency notes in banks.
After demonetization of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 currency notes by Modi government peoples are trying to convert their black money into white by buying gold, booking train and air tickets and exchanging it into other currency.
